<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-13 00:37 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3397 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GLF-GOLFNOTEBOOK-BOS &LR;      06-13 1455
