   BUSH-MAINE _ On an off day in Kennebunkport, we talk to the
locals about the prospects of a second stint as the summer White
House; will the down easters have to fight with Athens, Texas for
that honor? Bush owns a lake home there. The mayor says the town is
ready to expand the airport to accommodate Marine One, if
necessary. (Greenberger, Austin American-Statesman). 20-25.
