Warholium, for the fleeting nature of 118, which becomes 116 almost
immediately ( &UR; Steve Myers &LR; ); lovium for 118 and lustium for 116,
again, for the speed in which one becomes the other ( &UR; R.C. &LR; 
 &UR; Jones &LR; ); Herbcaenium ( &UR; John Ralston &LR; ) and Caenium ``because it's
