George W. Bush speaking at a fund-raiser for Rep. Jim Nussle in
Amana on Saturday. Bush began a four-day trip on Saturday to
publicly start his campaign. Bush's appearance in Iowa was the
first of nearly four days of explicitly political appearances, and
it had all the trappings of a full-scale political invasion.
(Andrea Mohin/New York Times Photo)
</P>
